---
title: Speedy Smoky Chorizo Orzo with Cheese, Peas and Rocket
description: Not to be confused with rice, orzo is actually a type of pasta. Whilst chorizo gives some of the flavour, we're also using smoky base paste, made with smoked paprika and smoked salt, to bring rich smoky flavour to your dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_RA_R46_W37_UK_F25200-4_Maiin_low_2-4d410793.jpg
